detail.name: Awakening to Super Saiyan Rosé
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Choose all cards with 《Earthling》 in their special traits in the Battle Areas and return them to their owners' hands. Then, if you returned 3 or more cards, draw 2 cards.

detail.name: 超サイヤ人ロゼへの覚醒
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】バトルエリアの特徴《地球人》を持つカードすべてを選び、持ち主の手札に戻す。その後、戻したカードが3枚以上の場合、カード2枚を引く。

faq.question: Do you also have to choose all of your cards with 《Earthling》 in their special traits for this card's skill?
faq.answer: Yes. You must choose all cards with 《Earthling》 in their special traits in the Battle Areas, including your cards.

faq.question: このカードは、自分の特徴《地球人》を持つカードもすべて選ばなくてはいけませんか？
faq.answer: はい、自分のものを含め、バトルエリアの特徴《地球人》を持つカードすべてを選ばなくてはいけません。
